        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on <hi rend="italic">Prehistoric Europe</hi>.</p>  
<p>Asks JG’s opinion of Daniel Mackintosh’s paper ["Results of a systematic survey of erratic blocks", <hi rend="italic">Q. J. Geol. Soc. Lond.</hi> 35 (1879): 425–53].</p> 
            <p>Comments on loess.</p>
            <p>Feels uneasy about streams of stone of Falkland Islands.</p>
